Agents are host/platform agnostic and communicate via open standards, they can
gurations in a secure way which protects sensitive payment
data and allows for privacy and choice of payment services that the payer would like to use. Payment
agents can also serve as connection points to existing payment systems which allows them to bridge
between current and future payment options.
